{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-189-tri-colouring-a-triangular-grid","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 189: Bojanje tri boje na trougačnoj mreži","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Razmotrite sledeću konfiguraciju petogona 64:</p>\n<img alt=\"64 triangles arranged to create larger triangle with side length of 8 triangles\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/tri-colouring-a-triangular-grid-1.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Želimo da obojimo svaki trougao jedne od tri boje: crvena, zelena ili plava, tako da susedni trougaoci ne imaju istu boju. Ovo obojavanje se naziva pravilno (ili legitimno). Ovde, dva trougla smatraju se susjedima ako dele ivicu. Zapamtite: ako dele samo vrh trougla, onda nisu susjedni.</p>\n<p>Na primer, ovde postoji važeće bojanje mreže iznad:</p>\n<img alt=\"colored grid of 64 triangles\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/tri-colouring-a-triangular-grid-2.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Boja C' dobijena iz nanošenja boje C rotacijom ili reflekcijom smatra se drugačijom od C, osim ako nisu apsolutno iste.</p>\n<p>Da li postoji koliko validnih različitih opcija bojenja za ovu konfiguraciju koja je iznad?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4291000cf542c50ff3c","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301825,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-189-tri-colouring-a-triangular-grid"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function triangularGridColoring() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\ntriangularGridColoring();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>triangularGridColoring()</code> treba da vrati <code>10834893628237824</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(triangularGridColoring(), 10834893628237824);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-101-to-200","dashedName":"problem-189-tri-colouring-a-triangular-grid","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":true,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-190-maximising-a-weighted-product","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-188-the-hyperexponentiation-of-a-number","id":"5900f4291000cf542c50ff3c","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-189-tri-colouring-a-triangular-grid"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}